title: 1936 Swing Time 2
description:
This is exactlly the same upload as 1936 Swing Time--without the "2."

I had to delete the original upload and intended to re-upload it right away.

On Mininova it went fine, but Pirate Bay was different.

After deleting, I always have to wait 24 hours before reloading.

But now, for some reason, they keep telling me it is already in the system, so I cannot reenter it.

This site is a troublesome place.

Even in the best of times they give me "wrong code" when I know it's wrong.
